When adding the column *Σ progress* into _filter results_ gadget this doesn't reflect the correct values. If you goto the issue view screen, you face the correct values of: *Estimated*, *Remaining* and *Logged*. However, when viewing this issue values via _filter results_ gadgets the *Estimated* time is not correct.

More details on attached screenshots. Bug verified with *Mozilla Firefox 3.6*.

*Steps to reproduce*:

# Insert test data into a fresh Jira Standalone instance;
# Activate the time tracking;
# Log work on a test issue;
# Create a test filter which refers to this issue;
# Add a _filter results_ gadget in _dashboard_;
# Choose the filter previously created and select *Σ progress* column;
# Review the gadget and see the unconformity between original estimated value displayed within filter and in the issue.

